{{Quote|A thousand fire wasps can take down a clestradon.|Common saying|<ref name="Empire 11">[[Empire 11|''Empire'' 11]]</ref>}}
'''Fire wasps''' were small, stinging [[Insect/Legends|insects]] with 6 clawed legs. They were able to fly with the use of 4 wings. Their antennae ended in sharp pointed stinger. The abdomen stinger had an embedded egg pod as well as poison, which would hatch inside the stung victim.<ref name="BHC" />

